WEBVTT

00:02.915 --> 00:04.961
PREVIOUSLY ON
"THE MENTALIST"...NO!

00:04.961 --> 00:06.093
[ GRUNTS ]

00:07.181 --> 00:10.184
Cho: WE BELIEVE THE ASSAILANT
IS THE SAME PERSON

00:10.184 --> 00:12.186
THAT KILLED
ATTORNEY OSVALDO ARDILES

00:12.186 --> 00:13.752
AND FORMER CALIFORNIA BUREAU
OF INVESTIGATION AGENT

00:13.752 --> 00:14.797
J.J. LaROCHE.

00:14.797 --> 00:16.364
GOOD TO SEE YOU,
GUYS.

00:16.364 --> 00:17.495
JUST GOT WORD THAT THE FBI
HAS OFFICIALLY HIRED YOU

00:17.495 --> 00:19.889
AS CONSULTANTS
FOR THE CASE.

00:19.889 --> 00:21.586
YOU'RE THE ONES WHO
FIRST FOUND OUT WE
WERE BEING TRACKED.

00:21.586 --> 00:23.197
YOU KNOW THIS CASE
BETTER THAN ANYBODY.

00:23.197 --> 00:24.676
ANYTHING ON
THE OTHER SEVEN SUSPECTS?

00:24.676 --> 00:26.591
A FEW LEADS.
NO BREAKTHROUGHS.

00:26.591 --> 00:28.550
WHICH LEAVES US
WITH HAIBACH.

00:35.644 --> 00:37.646
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

00:42.172 --> 00:44.522
[ BEEP ]HEY. I FELL ASLEEP.

00:44.522 --> 00:45.871
OH, I'M SORRY.
I JUST WANTED TO CHECK IN.

00:45.871 --> 00:47.134
I'M OUT HAVING
A DRINK WITH THE GUYS.

00:47.134 --> 00:49.179
[ SIGHS ]
WHAT HAPPENED WITH HUTTEN?

00:49.179 --> 00:50.963
IT'S NOT HIM.
I'LL EXPLAIN LATER.

00:50.963 --> 00:52.139
YOU GO BACK TO BED.

00:52.139 --> 00:53.792
YOU HAVING FUN?

00:53.792 --> 00:55.272
YEAH. YEAH, I AM.

00:55.272 --> 00:56.491
I'M GLAD.
IT'S GOOD FOR YOU.

00:56.491 --> 00:58.145
THANK YOU.

00:58.145 --> 00:59.450
I love you, babe.
You know that, right?

00:59.450 --> 01:01.017
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

01:01.017 --> 01:02.018
OKAY,
I'LL SEE YOU SOON.

01:02.018 --> 01:05.108
GOOD NIGHT.

01:05.108 --> 01:07.110
[ SIGHING ]

01:40.056 --> 01:42.102
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

01:44.539 --> 01:46.889
WELL, SHE AGREED
WITH YOU.

01:46.889 --> 01:48.891
SHE SAID I SHOULD BE OUT HAVING
A DRINK WITH YOU GUYS,

01:48.891 --> 01:50.066
SAID IT
WOULD BE GOOD FOR ME.

01:50.066 --> 01:51.415
SHE'S A SMART WOMAN.

01:51.415 --> 01:52.764
YEAH. YEAH, SHE IS.

01:52.764 --> 01:55.245
I'M A LUCKY MAN.
SHE'S THE BEST.

01:55.245 --> 01:57.508
A PRICE ABOVE RUBIES.
GRACE.

01:57.508 --> 01:59.945
TO GRACE. THANK YOU.

02:01.599 --> 02:05.125
YOU KNOW,
GRACE AND I, WE, UH...

02:05.125 --> 02:07.605
OH, WE ALWAYS THOUGHT
THAT YOU AND LISBON WOULD...

02:07.605 --> 02:09.564
YOU KNOW,
GET TOGETHER.

02:09.564 --> 02:10.826
HMM!

02:10.826 --> 02:11.827
JANE AND LISBON --
YEAH, RIGHT.

02:11.827 --> 02:13.220
I'M JUST SAYING.

02:13.220 --> 02:14.786
REMEMBER WHEN
YOU BOUGHT HER A PONY?

02:14.786 --> 02:17.572
YES, I DO.
I DO REMEMBER THAT.

02:17.572 --> 02:19.791
I WONDER
WHAT HAPPENED TO IT.

02:19.791 --> 02:21.793
OKAY, TWO MORE LONE STARS
AND A CLUB SODA.

02:21.793 --> 02:24.318
AND THE MAN AT THE POOL TABLE
WANTS ANOTHER GAME WITH YOU.

02:24.318 --> 02:26.102
WELL, CAN'T HE SEE
I'M HERE WITH MY FRIENDS?

02:26.102 --> 02:27.451
HE SEEMED
PRETTY DETERMINED,

02:27.451 --> 02:28.713
SAID HE'D MAKE IT
DOUBLE OR NOTHING.

02:28.713 --> 02:30.889
GO AND TAKE
THE MAN'S MONEY.

02:30.889 --> 02:32.500
I GOT TO
GET BACK TO MY WIFE.

02:32.500 --> 02:35.067
IT'S BEEN A PLEASURE.
GOOD NIGHT. WISH ME LUCK.

02:35.067 --> 02:37.679
GOOD LUCK. LET'S GET
SOMETHING TO EAT.

02:37.679 --> 02:39.463
YEAH, I THINK I SAW
A DRIVE-THROUGH ON THE WAY OVER.

02:39.463 --> 02:40.812
THEY HAD CHIMICHANGAS.

02:40.812 --> 02:43.337
SAME OLD RIGSBY.

02:48.820 --> 02:49.995
[ HORN HONKS ]

02:55.087 --> 02:58.743
YOU EVER THOUGHT ABOUT COMING
TO WORK AT THE FBI?

02:58.743 --> 03:00.441
[ SCOFFS ]
YOU KIDDING ME?

03:00.441 --> 03:03.313
BEEN DAYDREAMING ABOUT IT
FOR THE PAST SIX MONTHS.

03:03.313 --> 03:05.576
SO WHY NOT JOIN?

03:05.576 --> 03:07.839
YOU THINK
THEY'D HAVE ME?

03:07.839 --> 03:09.276
I KNOWTHEY WOULD.

03:09.276 --> 03:10.668
ABBOTT'S THE ONE
THAT WANTED ME TO ASK YOU --

03:10.668 --> 03:12.322
BOTH OF YOU, ACTUALLY.

03:12.322 --> 03:15.151
REALLY?
BOTH OF US? HMM.

03:15.151 --> 03:16.848
I DON'T KNOW.

03:16.848 --> 03:19.199
IT'S A PRETTY
24/7 TYPE OF GIG.

03:19.199 --> 03:20.896
SOMEONE'S GOT TO LOOK
AFTER THE KIDS.

03:20.896 --> 03:23.812
YOU SHOULD TALK ABOUT IT
WITH GRACE. THE OFFER'S THERE.

03:23.812 --> 03:25.901
NICE. OKAY.

03:25.901 --> 03:28.208
WELL, YOU WANT TO COME UP FOR
A DRINK, DISCUSS IT WITH GRACE?

03:28.208 --> 03:31.689
NO. BEST YOU TWO
TALK ABOUT IT ALONE.

03:31.689 --> 03:33.343
RIGHT. YEAH,
YOU'RE PROBABLY RIGHT.

03:35.127 --> 03:37.782
WHY'S THE DOOR
TO YOUR ROOM OPEN?

03:37.782 --> 03:39.436
I DON'T KNOW.

03:55.278 --> 03:57.280
GRACE?

04:02.111 --> 04:04.635
GRACE?

04:06.637 --> 04:09.292
GRACE? GRACE?!

04:10.554 --> 04:12.687
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

04:15.994 --> 04:18.867
KEYS ARE STILL ON THE TABLE.
SO IS HER WALLET.

04:19.737 --> 04:21.870
THERE'S A PERFECTLY REASONABLE
EXPLANATION FOR THIS, RIGHT?

04:21.870 --> 04:23.872
PLEASE TELL ME THERE'S ONE.DON'T JUMP TO CONCLUSIONS.

04:23.872 --> 04:25.700
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?CALLING HER CELL.

04:25.700 --> 04:28.833
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

04:35.275 --> 04:36.276
[ BEEP ]

04:37.842 --> 04:39.322
[ GROANS ]

04:39.322 --> 04:42.499
WHERE ARE YOU, GRACE?

04:45.067 --> 04:48.113
♪♪♪

04:48.113 --> 04:51.029
--Captions by VITAC--
www.vitac.com

04:56.600 --> 04:58.602
[ GASPS ]

05:01.997 --> 05:04.042
[ GROANS ]

05:06.958 --> 05:10.266
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

05:10.266 --> 05:13.487
HELLO?

05:15.532 --> 05:17.360
IS ANYBODY THERE?

05:21.146 --> 05:23.497
HELLO!

05:23.497 --> 05:25.150
RIGSBY AND JANE ARE WITH A TEAM
COMBING THROUGH THE MOTEL ROOM,

05:25.150 --> 05:26.630
BUT WE'VE GOT
NOTHING YET.

05:26.630 --> 05:27.675
THERE'S ABOUT A THOUSAND
DIFFERENT FINGERPRINTS

05:27.675 --> 05:28.806
AND DNA
ALL OVER EVERYTHING.

05:28.806 --> 05:31.331
I HATE HOTEL ROOMS.

05:31.331 --> 05:33.333
HOW'S WYLIE DOING WITH THE,
UH, CAMERA FOOTAGE

05:33.333 --> 05:35.073
THAT WE PULLED
FROM AROUND TOWN?[ SIGHS ]

05:35.073 --> 05:37.511
HE'S TRACED HER WHEREABOUTS
BEFORE SHE GOT TO THE MOTEL.

05:37.511 --> 05:38.512
ANYTHING USEFUL?

05:39.295 --> 05:41.428
NO.WELL, WHAT ELSE?

05:41.428 --> 05:43.604
AN S.U.V. LEAVING THE AREA
OF THE MOTEL

05:43.604 --> 05:46.084
AT THE ESTIMATED TIME
OF GRACE VAN PELT'S ABDUCTION.

05:47.434 --> 05:49.349
WAS HE ABLE TO GET
A LICENSE PLATE FROM IT?

05:49.349 --> 05:50.698
NO.

05:52.743 --> 05:54.266
[ SIGHS ]

05:54.266 --> 05:59.271
ALL RIGHT, PEOPLE,
LISTEN UP.

05:59.271 --> 06:03.798
WE ALREADY KNOW OUR PRIME
SUSPECT -- RICHARD HAIBACH.

06:03.798 --> 06:06.104
WE WERE ALREADY LOOKING AT HIM
FOR THE MURDERS

06:06.104 --> 06:10.718
OF EX-CBI AGENT J.J. LaROCHE
AND D.A. OSVALDO ARDILES.

06:10.718 --> 06:14.243
NOW GRACE VAN PELT IS GONE.
WHERE?

06:14.243 --> 06:15.940
WE DON'T KNOW.

06:15.940 --> 06:18.595
BUT WE'RE ASSUMING
THAT HAIBACH IS RESPONSIBLE.

06:18.595 --> 06:20.467
EXCUSE ME, AGENT ABBOTT?

06:20.467 --> 06:23.295
WE GOT A BOLO OUT.
WE ALERTED THE MEDIA.

06:23.295 --> 06:25.559
BUT HAIBACH
HAS ALREADY SLIPPED OUR TAIL

06:25.559 --> 06:27.212
IN COLORADO.

06:27.212 --> 06:29.911
HE'S IN THE WIND. HE KNOWS
WE'RE COMING AFTER HIM.

06:29.911 --> 06:31.216
AND HE WILL NOT
BE EASY TO FIND.

06:31.216 --> 06:32.957
AGENT ABBOTT,
THERE'S SOMEONE TO SEE YOU.

06:32.957 --> 06:36.961
BUT FIND HIM WE WILL.

06:36.961 --> 06:41.923
WHATEVER IT TAKES, PEOPLE.
FAILURE IS NOT AN OPTION HERE.

06:41.923 --> 06:44.229
FIND RICHARD HAIBACH.

06:47.798 --> 06:50.627
AGENT WYLIE,
WHAT DO YOU NEED?

06:50.627 --> 06:52.020
UH, WELL,
T-THERE'S A --

06:52.020 --> 06:53.413
THERE'S A MAN WHO CAME
TO RECEPTION DOWNSTAIRS.

06:53.413 --> 06:55.502
AN AGENT'S
BRINGING HIM UP.
SO?

06:55.502 --> 06:57.504
THE MAN SAYS
HE'S RICHARD HAIBACH.

06:57.504 --> 06:59.506
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS,
DOORS OPENS ]

07:03.814 --> 07:08.079
GO GET JANE
BACK HERE NOW.

07:10.125 --> 07:12.127
[ GRACE GRUNTING ]

07:15.217 --> 07:17.567
[ PANTING ]

07:17.567 --> 07:19.743
[ GROANS ]

07:19.743 --> 07:20.918
[ SIGHS ]

07:20.918 --> 07:23.007
HELLO?!

07:26.097 --> 07:29.579
IS ANYBODY HERE?!

07:50.295 --> 07:52.341
[ GRUNTING ]

08:06.007 --> 08:09.837
HELLO, AGENT LISBON,
MR. JANE.

08:09.837 --> 08:11.186
SIT DOWN, PLEASE.

08:11.186 --> 08:12.666
WHY ARE YOU HERE,
MR. HAIBACH?

08:12.666 --> 08:15.320
IS THAT
SOME KIND OF JOKE?

08:15.320 --> 08:16.887
I'VE BEEN IN FEAR
OF MY LIFE

08:16.887 --> 08:18.715
SINCE I LEARNED YOU WERE
STALKING ME AGAIN.

08:18.715 --> 08:22.153
WE'RE NOT STALKING YOU,
MR. HAIBACH.

08:22.153 --> 08:24.112
I KNEW THE MOMENT YOU STARTED
ASKING QUESTIONS ABOUT ME

08:24.112 --> 08:26.070
BEHIND MY BACK
TO PEOPLE AT MY JOB

08:26.070 --> 08:27.724
THAT YOU WERE
OUT TO GET ME.

08:27.724 --> 08:30.248
I ALREADY APOLOGIZED
TO YOU FOR THAT.

08:30.248 --> 08:31.728
OH, YOU APOLOGIZED,

08:31.728 --> 08:33.730
BUT THAT DIDN'T STOP
YOUR PLOTTING, DID IT?

08:33.730 --> 08:35.515
WE JUST HAD
A FEW QUESTIONS FOR YOU.

08:35.515 --> 08:38.735
REALLY? SO I'M NOT
YOUR NUMBER-ONE SUSPECT?

08:38.735 --> 08:41.259
HMM. THIS A GAME?

08:41.259 --> 08:42.913
NO GAME, MR. JANE.

08:42.913 --> 08:46.569
I AM, AS I SAID,
IN FEAR FOR MY LIFE.

08:46.569 --> 08:48.223
THINK ABOUT
WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

08:48.223 --> 08:51.269
THESE ARE PEOPLE
I CARE A LOT ABOUT.

08:51.269 --> 08:53.489
YES OR NO --

08:53.489 --> 08:56.144
A WARRANT HAS BEEN ISSUED
FOR MY ARREST, HASN'T IT?

08:56.144 --> 08:57.580
HOW DID YOU KNOW
ABOUT THAT?

08:57.580 --> 08:59.451
SO ONE HAS.

08:59.451 --> 09:01.366
I CALL THAT
AN EXECUTION ORDER,

09:01.366 --> 09:04.631
A LICENSE TO SHOOT ME DOWN
IN THE STREET LIKE A DOG.

09:04.631 --> 09:06.458
SO I'M HERE
TO PROVE MY INNOCENCE

09:06.458 --> 09:08.678
BEYOND ANY SHADOW
OF A DOUBT.

09:08.678 --> 09:10.027
DO YOU HAVE ANY KNOWLEDGE

09:10.027 --> 09:11.768
AS TO WHAT'S HAPPENED
TO GRACE VAN PELT?

09:11.768 --> 09:14.771
NO. I DON'T.

09:14.771 --> 09:16.120
HOW COULD I?

09:16.120 --> 09:18.296
TAKE A GUESS...FOR FUN.

09:18.296 --> 09:21.343
OKAY. SURE.

09:21.343 --> 09:22.692
I CAN MAKE
PLENTY OF GUESSES,

09:22.692 --> 09:26.043
BUT THAT'S ALL IT IS --
GUESSES.

09:26.043 --> 09:27.741
BUT...

09:27.741 --> 09:29.917
LET'S SEE.

09:29.917 --> 09:32.963
I'D GUESS SHE WAS...

09:32.963 --> 09:37.054
SOMEWHERE FAR AWAY,
OUT OF THE REACH OF YOUR HELP,

09:37.054 --> 09:39.056
OUT OF THE REACH
OF ANYONE'S HELP...

09:39.056 --> 09:41.363
ALONE AND TRAPPED...

09:41.363 --> 09:43.017
WITH TIME RUNNING OUT...

09:43.017 --> 09:46.237
IF I WERE TO GUESS,
I MEAN.

09:47.630 --> 09:50.241
SHOWING UP LIKE THIS
IS A BAD SIGN.

09:50.241 --> 09:53.070
90% OF THE TIME, IT MEANS
THE VICTIM'S ALREADY DEAD.

09:53.070 --> 09:55.333
WELL, I DON'T SEE ANY REASON
TO JUMP TO CONCLUSIONS.

09:55.333 --> 09:57.509
YOU'VE BEEN THROUGH THE QUANTICO
PROFILING COURSES, TOO.

09:57.509 --> 09:59.120
HIS PERFORMATIVE ASPECT
SUGGESTS

09:59.120 --> 10:00.687
THAT HE'S ALREADY
KILLED HER.

10:00.687 --> 10:03.515
HE'S JUST HERE TO GLOAT
WHEN WE FIND THE BODY.

10:06.780 --> 10:08.999
WHERE'S MY WIFE?!

10:08.999 --> 10:10.435
RIGSBY!

10:10.435 --> 10:11.523
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE
WITH HER?!AAH!

10:11.523 --> 10:13.134
COME ON, PLEASE.

10:13.134 --> 10:14.526
IF YOU HURT HER, I'LL KILL YOU!
YOU'RE AN ANIMAL!

10:14.526 --> 10:16.180
HURT HER?! LOOK AT ME!

10:16.180 --> 10:17.355
WHAT ABOUT ME?!

10:17.355 --> 10:18.443
I'LL KILL YOU!NO!

10:18.443 --> 10:20.358
STOP! NOT HERE!

10:20.358 --> 10:23.579
I WAS TORTURED BECAUSE YOU
PEOPLE THOUGHT I DESERVED IT,

10:23.579 --> 10:24.841
AND I DID NOTHING!

10:24.841 --> 10:26.538
I DID NOTHING!

10:26.538 --> 10:28.540
MY THUMB WAS CUT OFF
BECAUSE OF YOU!

10:28.540 --> 10:30.020
YOU PEOPLE
ARE THE ANIMALS!

10:30.020 --> 10:31.674
SIT DOWN, MR. HAIBACH.

10:46.689 --> 10:48.256
OKAY, RIGSBY, LISTEN.

10:48.256 --> 10:49.344
I UNDERSTAND HOW YOU'RE FEELING
RIGHT NOW. BELIEVE ME.

10:49.344 --> 10:51.346
BUT YOU ARE A FATHER,

10:51.346 --> 10:53.827
AND YOU HAVE CHILDREN
YOU NEED TO SEE GROW UP.

10:53.827 --> 10:55.742
BESIDES,
I THINK SHE'S STILL ALIVE.

10:55.742 --> 10:57.569
YOU DO?

10:57.569 --> 10:58.962
YES.

10:58.962 --> 11:01.443
HAIBACH'S REVENGE PLAN
WAS DISRUPTED BY GRACE

11:01.443 --> 11:03.401
WHEN SHE BROKE
HIS PHONE HACKS UP.

11:03.401 --> 11:05.447
HE REALIZED THEN

11:05.447 --> 11:08.624
THAT IT WAS ONLY A MATTER OF
TIME BEFORE WE TRACKED HIM DOWN.

11:08.624 --> 11:11.322
THIS IS HIM MAKING
THE BEST OF THE SITUATION.

11:11.322 --> 11:12.454
THEN WHY DID
HE COME HERE?

11:12.454 --> 11:15.022
TO GLOAT
AND WATCH US SQUIRM.

11:15.022 --> 11:18.373
AND HE PLANS TO MAKE US
LET HIM GO WHEN HE'S DONE.

11:18.373 --> 11:19.896
WE WON'T LET HIM
GET AWAY WITH IT.

11:23.117 --> 11:24.945
[ GRUNTS ]

11:28.383 --> 11:31.908
[ GRUNTS ]

11:31.908 --> 11:34.694
[ GROANS ]

12:17.084 --> 12:22.263
I WONDER IF
YOU'D MIND TELLING US

12:22.263 --> 12:25.048
WHERE YOU'VE BEEN
FOR THE LAST 24 HOURS.

12:25.048 --> 12:28.748
DO YOU OWN AN S.U.V. --
UH, MAYBE GRAY?

12:28.748 --> 12:30.271
NO, I DON'T.

12:30.271 --> 12:33.927
BUT THIS IS A VIDEO OF ME

12:33.927 --> 12:37.365
ON THE BUS
FROM DENVER TO AUSTIN.

12:37.365 --> 12:40.847
THIS IS MY BUS TICKET.

12:40.847 --> 12:42.892
AND THESE ARE THE NAMES

12:42.892 --> 12:45.939
OF THREE OF THE OTHER PASSENGERS
ON THE BUS AND THE BUS DRIVER.

12:45.939 --> 12:49.551
THEY CAN CONFIRM I WAS ON
THE BUS DURING THE ENTIRE TRIP.

12:49.551 --> 12:51.205
AND IN THIS ENVELOPE

12:51.205 --> 12:53.685
IS EVERYTHING YOU NEED TO KNOW
ABOUT MY WHEREABOUTS

12:53.685 --> 12:55.209
DURING THE TIME OF THE MURDERS
OF OSVALDO ARDILES

12:55.209 --> 12:57.211
AND J.J. LaROCHE.

12:57.211 --> 12:59.604
IT'S TABULATED
AND CROSS-REFERENCED.

12:59.604 --> 13:04.696
NOW, MY ATTORNEY IS SCHEDULED
TO ARRIVE, WELL, ANYTIME NOW.

13:06.176 --> 13:10.224
OKAY, HAIBACH'S ATTORNEY
IS GONNA BE HERE AT ANY SECOND,

13:10.224 --> 13:11.486
AND WE HAVE NO REASON
TO HOLD HIM.

13:11.486 --> 13:14.184
THIS IS HIS ALIBI.

13:14.184 --> 13:17.666
I WANT IT TURNED INSIDE OUT
AND TORN APART.

13:17.666 --> 13:20.016
FIND THE HOLES
AND SEE WHERE THEY LEAD.

13:21.409 --> 13:22.932
IN ANY EVENT,
THE EVIDENCE SUGGESTS

13:22.932 --> 13:25.717
THAT HAIBACH IS WORKING
WITH AN ACCOMPLICE.

13:25.717 --> 13:27.023
FIND OUT WHO THAT IS --

13:27.023 --> 13:29.591
SOMEBODY HE HANGS OUT WITH
AT WORK,

13:29.591 --> 13:31.680
SOMEBODY THAT HE MET
ON THE INTERNET,

13:31.680 --> 13:34.988
OLD FRIEND, NEW FRIEND.

13:34.988 --> 13:37.381
FIND THE ACCOMPLICE.

13:37.381 --> 13:40.645
AND DO IT QUICKLY. WE DON'T
HAVE THE LUXURY OF TIME.

13:40.645 --> 13:43.648
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

13:52.832 --> 13:54.181
OW!

13:54.181 --> 13:57.837
OHH, DAMN IT.

13:57.837 --> 13:59.229
[ GROANS ]

13:59.229 --> 14:02.885
[ SIGHS ]

14:11.459 --> 14:15.115
OKAY, HERE'S THE BUS ROUTE
FROM DENVER TO AUSTIN.

14:15.115 --> 14:16.594
HOW MANY MILES
IS THAT?

14:16.594 --> 14:20.860
UM...LET ME SEE.

14:20.860 --> 14:25.342
IT'S A LITTLE OVER
916 MILES.

14:25.342 --> 14:28.650
Ben: DADDY,
ARE YOU COMING HOME?

14:28.650 --> 14:30.043
[ RIGSBY SIGHS ]

14:30.043 --> 14:31.783
NOT FOR A LITTLE WHILE
LONGER, BUDDY.

14:31.783 --> 14:33.611
YOU'RE HAVING A GOOD TIME
WITH YOUR MOM, THOUGH, RIGHT?

14:33.611 --> 14:36.876
I GUESS.
SHE WORKS A LOT.

14:36.876 --> 14:39.095
IS GRACE THERE?

14:39.095 --> 14:40.967
UM...N-NO.

14:40.967 --> 14:43.795
SHE'S, UM --
SHE'S NOT HERE RIGHT NOW.

14:43.795 --> 14:47.103
SHE ALWAYS TELLS ME A STORY
BEFORE MY NAP.

14:47.103 --> 14:48.757
A STORY?

14:48.757 --> 14:50.672
ABOUT A NICE BULL WHO HAS TO
GO TO THE BULL FIGHT.

14:50.672 --> 14:54.197
FERDINAND.
WELL, HE GETS TO GO HOME.

14:54.197 --> 14:55.633
AND SMELL THE FLOWERS.

14:55.633 --> 14:57.070
YEAH.

14:57.070 --> 15:00.900
AND HE'S VERY HAPPY,
SITTING UNDER A BIG TREE.

15:00.900 --> 15:02.162
YEAH.

15:02.162 --> 15:05.687
OKAY, LOOK, I, UH...
I HAVE TO GO, BUDDY.

15:05.687 --> 15:10.779
WE'LL SPEAK VERY SOON, OKAY?
DADDY LOVES YOU.

15:10.779 --> 15:13.695
LOVE YOU, TOO. BYE, DAD.BYE, SON.

15:13.695 --> 15:15.479
[ SMOOCHES ][ SMOOCHES]

15:18.830 --> 15:20.136
EXCUSE ME.

15:24.532 --> 15:25.576
HEY.

15:28.579 --> 15:31.278
HAIBACH'S
LAWYER IS HERE.

15:31.278 --> 15:33.584
ABBOTT'S GONNA TRY AND STALL HER
FOR AS LONG AS HE CAN,

15:33.584 --> 15:36.979
BUT WE'RE PROBABLY
GONNA HAVE TO LET HAIBACH GO.

15:36.979 --> 15:40.287
WE DON'T HAVE ENOUGH CONCRETE
EVIDENCE TO HOLD HIM ON.

15:44.421 --> 15:45.945
OKAY.

15:52.734 --> 15:54.736
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

16:00.611 --> 16:03.440
JANE,
WHATEVER IT TAKES.

16:03.440 --> 16:06.966
PLEASE. I'M BEGGING YOU.
WE HAVE TO GET GRACE BACK.

16:13.320 --> 16:15.191
I SHOULD HAVE
BEEN CONTACTED

16:15.191 --> 16:17.846
THE MOMENT MY CLIENT
ARRIVED AT YOUR OFFICES.

16:17.846 --> 16:20.022
WELL, HE CAME
ON HIS OWN VOLITION.

16:20.022 --> 16:21.937
WE SIMPLY MET HIM
AS HE ASKED.

16:21.937 --> 16:24.766
WELL, I'D LIKE
TO SPEAK TO MY CLIENT ALONE.

16:24.766 --> 16:28.161
LOOK AT ME. YOU KNOW ME.
YOU KNOW WHAT I AM CAPABLE OF.

16:28.161 --> 16:31.120
SO IF YOU HAVE DONE ANYTHING
TO GRACE VAN PELT,

16:31.120 --> 16:32.730
I AM GONNA MAKE YOU PAY.

16:32.730 --> 16:34.515
EXCUSE ME. THE LAW SAYS YOU
CAN'T JUST CHARGE IN HERE --

16:34.515 --> 16:35.907
OH, DON'T YOU WORRY
ABOUT THE LAW.

16:35.907 --> 16:37.648
YOU NEED TO WORRY
ABOUT ME.

16:37.648 --> 16:39.433
IS THIS MAN COMPLETELY INSANE?AND NO MATTER WHERE YOU GO,

16:39.433 --> 16:41.217
I WILL FIND YOU,
AND I WILL MAKE YOU PAY.

16:41.217 --> 16:44.699
AGENT ABBOTT, IN ALL MY YEARS,
I HAVE NEVER WITNESSED --

16:44.699 --> 16:46.396
ALL RIGHT, THAT'S ENOUGH, JANE.UH, OKAY.

16:46.396 --> 16:47.832
SEE, WHAT YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND
ABOUT ME, RICH,

16:47.832 --> 16:48.920
IS I DON'T CARE.

16:48.920 --> 16:50.531
I'VE GOT NOTHING TO LOSE.

16:50.531 --> 16:52.141
I'VE BEEN PLAYING
WITH THE HOUSE MONEY FOR YEARS.

16:52.141 --> 16:54.665
AND IF I GO TO PRISON FOR
WHAT I DO TO YOU, I DON'T CARE.

16:54.665 --> 16:56.754
Abbott: OKAY, COME ON.
THAT'S ENOUGH.IF YOUR FRIEND DIES,
IT'S YOUR FAULT.

16:56.754 --> 16:58.408
THAT'S ENOUGH.YOU CAN'T BLAME ME!

16:58.408 --> 17:01.368
I HAD NOTHING TO DO WITH IT --
NOTHING AT ALL!

17:01.368 --> 17:03.848
WHAT IN THE HELL
WERE YOU DOING?

17:03.848 --> 17:04.849
THE UNEXPECTED.

17:04.849 --> 17:06.286
YEAH, IT WAS THAT.

17:06.286 --> 17:09.071
WELL, WE WANT HAIBACH
OUT OF HIS COMFORT ZONE,

17:09.071 --> 17:11.421
SO WE PUSH HIM
TO MAKE A MISTAKE.

17:11.421 --> 17:15.730
OKAY, NOW, WE BOTH KNOW I GIVE
YOU A LOT OF LATITUDE,

17:15.730 --> 17:17.906
BUT YOU JUST CRIMINALLY
THREATENED A SUSPECT

17:17.906 --> 17:20.604
IN FRONT OF HIS LAWYER
ON VIDEO.

17:20.604 --> 17:22.519
IT'S ADMISSIBLE IN COURT.

17:22.519 --> 17:24.782
HE CAME HERE WITH A PLAN, AND WE
DON'T KNOW WHAT THAT PLAN IS,

17:24.782 --> 17:26.088
BUT HE DOES.

17:26.088 --> 17:28.003
SO HE KNOWS THE PATTERN
IN ADVANCE.

17:28.003 --> 17:30.875
WE NEED TO BREAK
THAT PATTERN.

17:36.098 --> 17:38.100
[ GRUNTING ]

18:26.540 --> 18:28.585
DO YOU HAVE A MINUTE?

18:28.585 --> 18:32.546
JUST WAITING FOR MY CLIENT.
KNOCK YOURSELF OUT.

18:32.546 --> 18:34.852
WE JUST NEED
A LITTLE MORE TIME.

18:36.202 --> 18:38.073
REALLY?

18:38.073 --> 18:40.075
MY FIRM IS ALREADY
IN THE PROCESS OF GETTING

18:40.075 --> 18:43.426
THE DEPOSITIONS OF THE BUS'S
PASSENGERS AND THE DRIVER.

18:43.426 --> 18:45.646
WE'LL HAVE THEM ALL
BY THIS EVENING.

18:45.646 --> 18:47.952
RICHARD HAIBACH'S
WHEREABOUTS

18:47.952 --> 18:49.780
DURING THE ABDUCTION
OF YOUR ASSOCIATE

18:49.780 --> 18:52.609
CAN BE STATED
WITH ABSOLUTE CERTAINTY.

18:52.609 --> 18:53.958
[ SCOFFS ]

18:53.958 --> 18:56.135
YOU HAVE NO REASON
TO HOLD MY CLIENT.

18:56.135 --> 18:59.703
NOT YET,
BUT THE REASON IS THERE.

18:59.703 --> 19:01.792
NOW, EVEN YOU
HAVE TO SEE THAT.

19:01.792 --> 19:05.144
HE TOOK HER.
WE ALL KNOW THAT HE DID.

19:05.144 --> 19:06.667
THEN PROVE IT.

19:06.667 --> 19:08.799
OTHERWISE,
YOU HAVE TO LET MY CLIENT GO.

19:08.799 --> 19:10.497
THAT'S THE WAY
THE LAW WORKS.

19:10.497 --> 19:13.674
HE'LL KILL HER IF WE LET HIM GO,
IF HE HASN'T ALREADY.

19:13.674 --> 19:15.023
DO YOU REALIZE THAT?

19:15.023 --> 19:17.243
LOOK, DON'T TRY
AND MAKE ME FEEL GUILTY.

19:17.243 --> 19:19.506
I'VE BEEN DOING THIS
A LONG TIME,

19:19.506 --> 19:21.464
AND MY JOB AS A LAWYER
IS TO DEFEND MY CLIENT.

19:21.464 --> 19:23.249
THAT'S WHY
PEOPLE PAY ME.

19:23.249 --> 19:26.165
SO YOU CAN GIVE ME
WHATEVER SOB STORY YOU WANT,

19:26.165 --> 19:28.471
BUT WE BOTH KNOW
YOU'VE GOT NOTHING.

19:28.471 --> 19:30.952
WHATEVER HAPPENS
IS ON YOUR HEAD.

19:30.952 --> 19:32.649
THAT IS INACCURATE,

19:32.649 --> 19:35.609
UNPROFESSIONAL,
AND DISRESPECTFUL.

19:35.609 --> 19:38.394
I'M DOING MY JOB.
DON'T MAKE ME DO YOURS.

19:43.399 --> 19:46.750
HELLO?!

19:46.750 --> 19:50.058
IS ANYBODY OUT HERE?!

19:50.058 --> 19:52.582
ANYBODY OUT HERE?!

19:52.582 --> 19:54.584
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

20:05.900 --> 20:07.206
[ VEHICLE APPROACHES ]

20:07.206 --> 20:09.425
[ COUNTRY MUSIC PLAYING]

20:14.300 --> 20:17.303
[ SIGHS ]

20:17.303 --> 20:19.957
HEY. HEY.

20:19.957 --> 20:21.916
HEY!

20:21.916 --> 20:22.960
HEY.

20:25.180 --> 20:27.356
ARE YOU OKAY?[ MUSIC STOPS ]

20:27.356 --> 20:29.010
DO YOU HAVE A PHONE?
I JUST --WELL, LOOK,
WERE YOU IN AN ACCIDENT?

20:29.010 --> 20:31.012
I-I JUST NEED A PHONE.
PLEASE, DO YOU HAVE A PHONE?

20:31.012 --> 20:32.318
OKAY, OKAY, OKAY.
OKAY, HERE. HERE IT IS.

20:32.318 --> 20:34.581
[ SIGHS ]
THANK YOU.

20:34.581 --> 20:36.452
[ CELLPHONE BEEPING ]

20:36.452 --> 20:38.498
IS THERE COVERAGE?I DON'T KNOW.

20:38.498 --> 20:39.803
IT'S KIND OF SPOTTY
OUT HERE.

20:39.803 --> 20:41.588
Y-YOU'RE HALF-FROZEN.
WHERE'S YOU CAR?

20:41.588 --> 20:42.806
WHERE'S
THE POLICE STATION?

20:42.806 --> 20:44.112
UH, TAOS, I GUESS.

20:44.112 --> 20:46.332
THAT'S, UM,
45 MINUTES NORTH OF HERE.

20:46.332 --> 20:47.594
OR THERE'S A RANGER STATION
ABOUT A HALF AN HOUR SOUTH.

20:47.594 --> 20:49.509
WHERE'S
THE NEAREST PHONE?

20:49.509 --> 20:51.075
WELL, MY CABIN,
I GUESS.

20:51.075 --> 20:52.468
OKAY, OKAY.
I NEED YOU TO TAKE ME THERE.

20:52.468 --> 20:54.644
CAN YOU TAKE ME THERE?
IT'S IMPORTANT.

20:54.644 --> 20:56.342
JUST TAKE ME THERE RIGHT NOW.YEAH, YEAH. ALL RIGHT.
GET IN, GET IN, GET IN.

20:56.342 --> 20:59.040
OKAY.

20:59.040 --> 21:00.650
OH, YOU MUST BE FROZEN.

21:00.650 --> 21:03.349
YEAH.

21:06.874 --> 21:09.485
I'VE LOOKED INTO HAIBACH'S KNOWN
ASSOCIATES. IT'S A SHORT LIST.

21:09.485 --> 21:12.923
HE WAS A LONER AT WORK
AND IN HIS PRIVATE LIFE.

21:12.923 --> 21:14.273
HE'S GOT AN OLDER SISTER
NAMED HAZEL

21:14.273 --> 21:16.057
THAT I HAVEN'T BEEN
ABLE TO CONTACT.

21:16.057 --> 21:18.407
I SENT LOCAL P.D. TO CHECK HER
ADDRESS. SHOULD BE HEARING SOON.

21:18.407 --> 21:21.062
DUBIN KNOWS WE DON'T HAVE ENOUGH
TO CHARGE HAIBACH.

21:21.062 --> 21:22.324
WE HAVE TO
LET HIM WALK.

21:24.674 --> 21:26.110
I'LL TELL RIGSBY.

21:26.110 --> 21:27.373
KEEP HIM TOGETHER, OKAY?

21:29.418 --> 21:33.074
YOU THINK IF I TALK
TO THIS LAWYER WOMAN TO WOMAN,

21:33.074 --> 21:34.597
IT WOULD HAVE ANY EFFECT?

21:34.597 --> 21:37.774
DON'T WASTE YOUR TIME.

21:44.999 --> 21:49.177
OKAY, HERE WE ARE.
HOME SWEET HOME.

21:49.177 --> 21:50.657
COME ON, DARLING,
LET'S GET YOU INSIDE.

21:50.657 --> 21:53.312
GET YOU SOMETHING WARM.OKAY. THANKS.

21:53.312 --> 21:56.837
[ SIGHS ]

22:02.712 --> 22:05.411
[ SIGHS ]

22:05.411 --> 22:08.718
OKAY, NOW, MIND THOSE STEPS,
'CAUSE THOSE ARE SLIPPERY.

22:08.718 --> 22:12.853
[ SIGHS ]

22:12.853 --> 22:15.986
HEY, SHUT THE DOOR BEHIND YOU.
DON'T LET THE HEAT OUT.

22:15.986 --> 22:18.337
PHONE'S IN THE BEDROOM.
I'LL GO GET IT.

22:20.904 --> 22:22.558
NO ELECTRICITY, HUH?

22:22.558 --> 22:24.081
OH, LORD.
BLESS YOUR HEART. NO.

22:24.081 --> 22:25.822
THE POLES DON'T COME OUT
THIS FAR.

22:25.822 --> 22:28.216
THEN HOW DO YOU
HAVE A PHONE?

22:28.216 --> 22:29.696
I DON'T.[ GUN COCKS ]

22:29.696 --> 22:32.002
I LIED.

22:35.963 --> 22:37.312
[ TELEPHONES RINGING ]

22:37.312 --> 22:38.618
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

22:49.846 --> 22:51.195
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

22:51.195 --> 22:52.849
OKAY, KIDS, TIME'S UP.

22:52.849 --> 22:54.851
PUT YOUR PENCILS DOWN.

22:54.851 --> 22:56.853
WE'RE PROCESSING
YOUR CLIENT RIGHT NOW.

22:56.853 --> 23:00.204
I'LL TELL MY CAR
TO PULL AROUND.

23:03.860 --> 23:07.342
OKAY, THAT'S RIGHT.
PULL IT TIGHT.

23:07.342 --> 23:08.474
USE YOU TEETH.

23:14.784 --> 23:16.960
OKAY.

23:16.960 --> 23:18.658
SO YOU JUST STAY HERE,
AND YOU DON'T CAUSE TROUBLE.

23:18.658 --> 23:20.181
RICHARD'S GONNA KNOW WHAT TO DO
WITH YOU WHEN HE GETS HERE.

23:20.181 --> 23:21.617
[ SHIVERING ]

23:21.617 --> 23:23.184
PLEASE, DO YOU HAVE
ANYTHING HOT TO DRINK?

23:23.184 --> 23:25.404
[ SIGHS, SNIFFLES ]

23:25.404 --> 23:28.363
I GOT SOME COFFEE
I CAN HEAT UP.

23:28.363 --> 23:31.235
[ SIGHS ]
THAT'D BE GREAT. THANKS.

23:31.235 --> 23:32.715
AND NO TRICKS.
[ SIGHS ]

23:32.715 --> 23:35.457
NO TRICKS.

23:43.813 --> 23:45.554
MY NAME'S GRACE,
BY THE WAY.

23:45.554 --> 23:48.078
DON'T YOU TRY AND MAKE FRIENDS,
'CAUSE I'M NOT STUPID.

23:48.078 --> 23:51.604
OKAY. SORRY.

24:00.134 --> 24:02.223
RICHARD'S YOUR BROTHER,
ISN'T HE?

24:05.269 --> 24:09.012
IT WAS JUST THE TWO OF YOU,
WASN'T IT?

24:09.012 --> 24:10.797
NO OTHER SISTERS
OR BROTHERS?

24:10.797 --> 24:12.189
YEP.

24:14.627 --> 24:16.629
YOU'RE OLDER?

24:16.629 --> 24:18.457
MM-HMM.
THREE YEARS.

24:21.764 --> 24:27.074
SOMETHING HAPPENED
WHEN YOU WERE KIDS, DIDN'T IT?

24:27.074 --> 24:28.597
SOMETHING BAD.

24:28.597 --> 24:31.644
[ WIND HOWLING ]

24:31.644 --> 24:35.952
RICHARD HAD IT
SO HARD GROWING UP.

24:35.952 --> 24:38.433
YOU PEOPLE
DIDN'T UNDERSTAND THAT.

24:38.433 --> 24:40.304
IT WASN'T HIS FAULT.

24:40.304 --> 24:43.220
WHAT WAS SO HARD?

24:43.220 --> 24:46.876
OUR MOTHER [SIGHS]
RUN AWAY,

24:46.876 --> 24:49.226
LEFT US BOTH
WITH A DRUNK.

24:49.226 --> 24:52.708
AND HE DID THINGS
TO RICHARD.

24:52.708 --> 24:55.058
[ SIGHS ]
THINGS HE SHOULDN'T HAVE.

24:57.496 --> 25:00.847
WASN'T HIS FAULT.

25:00.847 --> 25:04.851
[ SNIFFLES ]
I DIDN'T PROTECT HIM.

25:04.851 --> 25:08.985
HIS BIG SISTER...
DIDN'T PROTECT HIM.

25:08.985 --> 25:11.510
YOU WERE JUST A LITTLE GIRL.
IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT.

25:11.510 --> 25:13.120
DON'T YOU PRETEND SYMPATHY.[ THUD ]

25:13.120 --> 25:15.905
YOU PEOPLE ARE BAD
AS MY FATHER --

25:15.905 --> 25:17.820
WHAT YOU DID TO RICHARD.

25:17.820 --> 25:21.824
HE WASN'T HURTING NOBODY,
BUT YOU PUSHED AND YOU PUSHED.

25:21.824 --> 25:24.392
AND NOW, MISS CUTIE PIE,
IT IS YOUWHO'S GONNA BE HURT.

25:24.392 --> 25:26.742
'CAUSE THAT'S ONLY FAIR.

25:28.309 --> 25:31.355
[ SIGHS ]

25:33.967 --> 25:36.099
Dubin: THE NEXT STEP WILL BE
TAKING THE FBI TO COURT.

25:36.099 --> 25:38.624
WE HAVE GROUNDS
FOR A STRONG SUIT.

25:38.624 --> 25:41.801
WILL THEY ALL
LOSE THEIR JOBS?

25:41.801 --> 25:43.803
WELL, SURE,
BUT THERE'S POTENTIAL

25:43.803 --> 25:46.414
FOR A LARGE SETTLEMENT,
AS WELL --

25:46.414 --> 25:47.937
EIGHT-FIGURES LARGE.

25:47.937 --> 25:50.113
I DON'T CARE ABOUT MONEY.

25:50.113 --> 25:52.594
I JUST WANT TO MAKE SURE
PATRICK JANE SUFFERS.

25:52.594 --> 25:54.553
I WANT HIM TO SUFFER
A LOT.

25:56.511 --> 25:58.557
HEY, Y-YOU MISSED
THE ON-RAMP.

25:58.557 --> 26:01.777
T-THIS IS THE WRONG WAY.

26:01.777 --> 26:03.300
N-NO,
YOU DON'T HAVE TO STOP.

26:03.300 --> 26:05.128
YOU CAN JUST TAKE
THE NEXT RIGHT.

26:12.396 --> 26:14.224
HELLO, AGAIN.

26:14.224 --> 26:16.357
HAIBACH, COUNSELOR.

26:26.541 --> 26:29.152
JANE AND RIGSBY
ARE MISSING.

26:29.152 --> 26:31.154
WE FOUND DUBIN'S
LIVERY DRIVER

26:31.154 --> 26:33.548
LOCKED UP
IN A DOWNSTAIRS CLOSET.

26:33.548 --> 26:36.551
SIR, HONESTLY, I DIDN'T KNOW
ANYTHING ABOUT THIS.

26:36.551 --> 26:38.509
WE HAD NOTHING
TO DO WITH IT.

26:38.509 --> 26:40.686
BUT WE WOULD HAVE,
IF THEY ASKED.

26:40.686 --> 26:43.689
[ SCOFFS ] NOW, I'M SURE YOU
FIND THAT BRAVE AND NOBLE,

26:43.689 --> 26:45.516
BUT IT'S NOT.

26:45.516 --> 26:48.868
YOU'RE FEDERAL AGENTS, AND I
EXPECT YOU TO BEHAVE AS SUCH.

26:48.868 --> 26:52.393
OTHERWISE,
I HAVE NO USE FOR YOU.

26:52.393 --> 26:53.916
NOW GET OUT OF MY OFFICE.

27:00.575 --> 27:02.708
FISCHER.

27:04.361 --> 27:07.495
FIND THEM. RIGHT NOW.

27:15.546 --> 27:16.722
GET OUT.

27:16.722 --> 27:18.506
OH, YOU PEOPLE
ARE INSANE.

27:18.506 --> 27:20.247
YOU'RE NEVER GONNA
GET AWAY WITH THIS.

27:20.247 --> 27:22.641
LISTEN, HE TOOK MY WIFE.
WHATEVER HE GETS, HE DESERVES.

27:22.641 --> 27:24.164
NOW GO.

27:26.079 --> 27:28.734
UH, COUNSELOR.

27:28.734 --> 27:29.952
HERE.

27:31.084 --> 27:32.738
YOU SHOULD PROBABLY THINK
ABOUT YOUR CHOICE OF CLIENTS

27:32.738 --> 27:35.523
ON YOUR LITTLE WALK
BACK TO AUSTIN.

27:35.523 --> 27:37.220
OH.

27:39.266 --> 27:42.835
LOOKS GOOD.

27:44.750 --> 27:48.275
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

28:02.376 --> 28:04.726
I'M A MOTHER, YOU KNOW.

28:04.726 --> 28:08.295
I HAVE A BABY GIRL.
HER NAME'S MADDY.

28:08.295 --> 28:11.646
CUT IT OUT.
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR ABOUT IT.

28:11.646 --> 28:13.343
WE NAMED HER
AFTER MY GRANDMOTHER.

28:13.343 --> 28:15.041
HER NAME'S
REALLY MADELEINE,

28:15.041 --> 28:17.304
BUT SHE LOOKS MORE
LIKE A MADDY, YOU KNOW?

28:18.653 --> 28:21.482
SHE SHOULDN'T HAVE TO GROW UP
WITHOUT A MOTHER, SHOULD SHE?

28:21.482 --> 28:24.746
YOU JUST DON'T GET IT,
DO YOU?[ GUN COCKS ]

28:24.746 --> 28:27.575
THIS ISN'T ABOUT YOU.
THIS IS ABOUT ME AND RICHARD.

28:27.575 --> 28:31.057
EVERYBODY HAS LOOKED DOWN ON US.
IT'S LIKE WE WERE NOTHING.

28:31.057 --> 28:32.754
BUT NOW THEY'LL SEE.

28:32.754 --> 28:35.365
HAZEL AND RICHARD ARE GONNA GET
THE ATTENTION THEY DESERVE.

28:35.365 --> 28:37.890
HEY.

28:37.890 --> 28:41.241
HEY.

28:41.241 --> 28:42.503
WAIT A MINUTE.

28:43.678 --> 28:46.159
WHAT WERE
YOU JUST DOING?

28:46.159 --> 28:47.595
PUT YOUR HANDS UP.

28:47.595 --> 28:50.293
PUT 'EM UP!

28:50.293 --> 28:52.078
OH, YOU LITTLE BITCH!

28:52.078 --> 28:53.775
[ GRUNTS ]
OHH.

28:53.775 --> 28:56.909
YOU WERE, OH,
JUST MAKING ALL NICE.

28:56.909 --> 28:58.301
AND THE WHOLE TIME,

28:58.301 --> 29:01.391
YOU'RE JUST LYING,
LYING, LYING TO ME.

29:01.391 --> 29:02.958
AAH! HAZEL, THAT'S TOO TIGHT.
YOU'RE HURTING ME.

29:02.958 --> 29:05.308
WELL, THAT'S WHAT YOU DESERVE,
ISN'T IT, YOU BIG LIAR?!

29:05.308 --> 29:07.484
AND YOU KNOW WHAT --
WHEN RICHARD GETS HERE,

29:07.484 --> 29:09.312
I'M GONNA TELL HIM
ALL ABOUT THIS,

29:09.312 --> 29:11.445
AND HE'S GONNA BE SO MAD.

29:11.445 --> 29:13.012
YOU KNOW WHAT?

29:13.012 --> 29:15.754
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR
ANY MORE OF YOUR WORDS!

29:26.112 --> 29:28.114
WHERE IS SHE?!
WHERE'S MY WIFE?

29:28.114 --> 29:29.245
YOU'RE WASTING
YOUR TIME.

29:29.245 --> 29:30.943
[ GRUNTS, GROANS ]

29:30.943 --> 29:32.118
WHERE IS SHE?!

29:32.118 --> 29:34.076
I WON'T TELL YOU
WHERE SHE IS.

29:34.076 --> 29:35.643
[ GRUNTS ][ TIRES SCREECH ]

29:35.643 --> 29:37.906
YOU CAN KILL ME.
IT WON'T MAKE A DIFFERENCE.

29:37.906 --> 29:38.951
[ GRUNTS ]

29:38.951 --> 29:40.779
AAH!

29:40.779 --> 29:42.041
I'M GONNA DIE! I'M GONNA DIE!Patrick: WHOA, WHOA.

29:42.041 --> 29:43.782
Rigsby:
DOES THAT CHANGE ANYTHING?

29:43.782 --> 29:46.610
N-NO! STOP! STOP!
[ SCREAMING ]

29:47.263 --> 29:50.310
OHH!

29:51.398 --> 29:54.618
[ TIRES SQUEAL ]

29:58.187 --> 30:00.189
[ GROANS ]

30:00.189 --> 30:02.235
ANSWER ME.
WHERE IS SHE?

30:02.235 --> 30:03.845
[ GROANS ]Patrick: RIGSBY.

30:03.845 --> 30:05.455
WHERE'S MY WIFE?!

30:05.455 --> 30:08.154
WHOA, RIGSBY! CALM DOWN,
CALM DOWN. JUST COUNT TO 10.

30:08.154 --> 30:11.026
JUST COUNT TO 10.
COUNT TO 10.WHERE'S MY WIFE?

30:11.026 --> 30:12.158
AAH!

30:12.158 --> 30:13.942
NO, WE DON'T
WANT TO KILL HIM.

30:13.942 --> 30:15.944
WE JUST WANT TO MAKE HIM TALK.
I HAVE A PLAN.

30:15.944 --> 30:17.641
THIS ISN'T ABOUT
ONE OF YOUR PLANS.

30:17.641 --> 30:20.470
SEE, YOU NEED TO JUST STOP
AND JUST TALK TO ME, OKAY?

30:20.470 --> 30:22.385
TALK TO ME, RIGSBY.[ HAIBACH GROANING ]

30:22.385 --> 30:23.734
THERE'S ANOTHER WAY.

30:23.734 --> 30:26.041
I'M GONNA
MAKE HIM TALK.

30:26.041 --> 30:28.043
NO, RIGSBY.[ SCREAMING ]

30:28.043 --> 30:29.305
NO! NO, RIGSBY.

30:29.305 --> 30:30.437
YOU DON'T
WANT TO DO THIS.

30:30.437 --> 30:34.006
AW.[ CRYING, GAGGING ]

30:34.006 --> 30:36.008
I GOT NO TIME
TO PLAY GAMES HERE.

30:36.008 --> 30:37.792
I WANT ANSWERS![ COUGHING ]

30:39.446 --> 30:42.579
ANSWER ME!
WHERE'S MY WIFE?!

30:42.579 --> 30:44.016
LAST CHANCE!

30:46.540 --> 30:49.456
OKAY, YOU NEED TO
LET ME HANDLE THIS.

30:49.456 --> 30:51.588
NO, THERE'S NO TIME.
I HAVE TO FIND GRACE.

30:51.588 --> 30:53.242
YOU'RE GONNA SET FIRE
TO THE ONLY PERSON

30:53.242 --> 30:54.635
THAT CAN TELL US
WHERE SHE IS.

30:54.635 --> 30:55.941
W-WHAT IS
THE POINT OF THAT?

30:55.941 --> 30:57.594
WHAT IS
THAT GONNA PROVE?

30:57.594 --> 30:58.813
Richard:
DROP SOMETHING?

31:00.728 --> 31:01.990
NO, DON'T.
DROP THE FLARE.

31:01.990 --> 31:03.078
GET RID OF THE FLARE!

31:03.078 --> 31:04.558
OKAY, OKAY.

31:04.558 --> 31:07.648
GIVE ME YOUR COAT.

31:07.648 --> 31:09.432
PUT THE VEST
IN THE TRUNK.

31:09.432 --> 31:12.044
YOU, JANE,
YOU'RE GONNA DRIVE.

31:12.044 --> 31:14.524
LET'S GO.

31:14.524 --> 31:15.656
EASY.

31:17.179 --> 31:20.139
MAN WAS CURIOUS
ABOUT HIS WIFE.

31:20.139 --> 31:21.880
I'M GONNA SATISFY
THAT CURIOSITY.

31:21.880 --> 31:23.838
GET IN.

31:37.243 --> 31:39.593
THEY FOUND DUBIN
ON OLD HIGHWAY 29.

31:39.593 --> 31:41.029
MAYBE THEY'RE HEADED
FOR HILL COUNTRY.

31:41.029 --> 31:42.422
HAIBACH COULD HAVE
A PLACE OUT THERE.

31:42.422 --> 31:43.902
YEAH, I DON'T THINK SO.

31:43.902 --> 31:45.773
I'VE HAD AGENTS SEARCHING
EVERY INCH OF THE STATE.

31:45.773 --> 31:47.035
I THINK THEY'RE
OUT OF TEXAS.

31:47.035 --> 31:49.559
UM, I HAVE AN IDEA.

31:49.559 --> 31:52.214
MAYBE. NEW MEXICO.

31:52.214 --> 31:54.477
UP IN
THE SANGRE DE CRISTO MOUNTAINS.

31:54.477 --> 31:55.522
WHY DO YOU THINK THAT?

31:55.522 --> 31:56.740
WELL,
I THOUGHT I'D TRY COMING

31:56.740 --> 31:57.916
FROM A DIFFERENT ANGLE,
YOU KNOW?

31:57.916 --> 31:59.221
'CAUSE EVERYONE
KEPT SAYING

31:59.221 --> 32:01.049
HOW HAIBACH WAS BEING
SO CAREFUL AND STUFF.

32:01.049 --> 32:03.704
SO FIRST I LOOKED INTO WHERE
HAIBACH WAS BORN AND GREW UP.

32:03.704 --> 32:05.184
OH, LET ME GUESS --
NEW MEXICO?

32:05.184 --> 32:06.533
NO, BUT HE HAD
GRANDPARENTS THERE,

32:06.533 --> 32:07.882
SPENT TIME THERE
AS A CHILD.

32:07.882 --> 32:09.928
HE LIKED IT,
RETURNED WHENEVER HE COULD.

32:09.928 --> 32:12.800
[ KEYBOARD CLACKING ]IN FACT, HE WROTE HIS THESIS
IN COLLEGE

32:12.800 --> 32:15.803
ON THE PUEBLO PEOPLE CULTURE,
WHICH IS CENTERED IN NEW MEXICO.

32:15.803 --> 32:18.632
HE -- HE DIDN'T ACTUALLY DO TOO
WELL ON THE PAPER, ACTUALLY --

32:18.632 --> 32:20.590
WE DON'T
NEED TO KNOW THAT.

32:20.590 --> 32:22.462
OH, OKAY. RIGHT.

32:22.462 --> 32:24.725
SO -- SO THEN I STARTED LOOKING
INTO HIS SHOPPING PROFILE,

32:24.725 --> 32:28.555
FOCUSING ON TRAVEL, BOOKS,
CAMPING GEAR, STUFF LIKE THAT.

32:28.555 --> 32:30.774
AND THERE WERE PURCHASES
DESIGNED FOR COLD AND SNOW.

32:30.774 --> 32:33.864
BUT HE LIVES IN COLORADO.
THAT'S COLD AND SNOWY.

32:33.864 --> 32:36.171
RIGHT, BUT HE ALSO BOUGHT TRAVEL
BOOKS FOR TAOS AND ALBUQUERQUE,

32:36.171 --> 32:37.477
BOTH IN NEW MEXICO.

32:37.477 --> 32:38.957
OKAY, YOU MAY BE
ONTO SOMETHING.

32:38.957 --> 32:40.654
WE'LL LOOK INTO IT.WAIT. THAT'S NOT ALL.

32:40.654 --> 32:42.090
ON A HUNCH,
I CALLED THE NEW TENANT

32:42.090 --> 32:43.874
WHO MOVED INTO
HAZEL HAIBACH'S APARTMENT.

32:43.874 --> 32:45.964
I ASKED HER IF SHE'D FORGOTTEN
ANYTHING, NEEDED IT MAILED.

32:45.964 --> 32:47.574
TURNED OUT SHE DID.

32:47.574 --> 32:49.706
THE ADDRESS SHE GAVE
WAS A P.O. BOX IN SANTA FE.

32:49.706 --> 32:51.795
NEW MEXICO.AT THE FOOT OF
THE SANGRE DE CRISTO MOUNTAINS.

32:51.795 --> 32:53.232
YEAH.
GREAT.

32:53.232 --> 32:55.669
GET THE SATELLITES
LOOKING IN THE AREA.

32:55.669 --> 32:57.366
I'LL PUT IN
A REQUEST TO GET A DRONE UP.

32:57.366 --> 32:59.542
IF THEY ARE OUT THERE,
I THINK WE CAN FIND THEM.

33:04.417 --> 33:08.073
SHE GOT AWAY.
THAT'S MY GIRL.

33:10.031 --> 33:12.686
THAT'S ALL RIGHT.
BET I CAN FIND HER.

33:12.686 --> 33:14.166
GET BACK OUT TO THE CAR.

33:34.664 --> 33:36.492
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

33:36.492 --> 33:39.147
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

33:39.147 --> 33:40.844
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

33:44.196 --> 33:46.024
[ BEEPING ]

33:50.680 --> 33:51.855
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

33:51.855 --> 33:53.161
Hazel:
RICHARD'S COMING.

33:53.161 --> 33:54.858
HEY, DO YOU THINK
IT WAS BY CHANCE

33:54.858 --> 33:56.034
THAT I PICKED YOU UP?

33:56.034 --> 33:58.514
THAT TOLD ME
WHEN YOU ESCAPED.

33:58.514 --> 34:01.735
I WAS COMING FOR YOU,
STUPID.

34:03.737 --> 34:06.261
WE THINK
WE MAY HAVE FOUND THE PLACE

34:06.261 --> 34:08.263
THAT GRACE VAN PELT
IS BEING HELD.

34:08.263 --> 34:11.223
IT'S A SEASONAL CABIN UP NEAR
THE EDGE OF THE TREE LINE.

34:11.223 --> 34:14.487
YOU HAVE EVIDENCE OF OCCUPATION?
FIRMEVIDENCE?

34:14.487 --> 34:16.358
SMOKE COMING OUT OF THE CHIMNEY,
GOING BACK SIX WEEKS.

34:16.358 --> 34:19.492
SAME TIME HAZEL HAIBACH
LEFT SACRAMENTO.

34:19.492 --> 34:21.276
AND THERE'S A GRAY S.U.V.
PARKED NEXT TO THE BUILDING.

34:21.276 --> 34:23.800
IT ALL MATCHES UP.THIS MUST BE THE PLACE.

34:23.800 --> 34:27.108
OKAY.

34:27.108 --> 34:29.415
I'LL CALL THE CHOPPER.
WE'LL BE THERE IN AN HOUR.

34:42.297 --> 34:45.300
Richard:
PULL OVER AND STOP.

34:49.826 --> 34:51.306
[ ENGINE SHUTS OFF ]

34:51.306 --> 34:53.874
WE'RE HERE. GET OUT.

34:53.874 --> 34:56.050
THAT'S WHERE GRACE IS?

34:56.050 --> 34:58.096
GET OUT AND SEE.

34:58.096 --> 35:00.489
AND YOUR SISTER, HAZEL, RIGHT?
SHE'S THERE, TOO?

35:00.489 --> 35:02.012
WHAT?

35:02.012 --> 35:03.753
WELL, YOU DIDN'T THINK
WE KNEW?

35:03.753 --> 35:05.364
DO WE LOOK
THAT STUPID TO YOU?

35:05.364 --> 35:08.149
SHUT UP
AND GET OUT OF THE CAR.

35:08.149 --> 35:10.151
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

35:10.151 --> 35:12.066
NO.

35:12.066 --> 35:16.331
[ GUN COCKS ]OUT OF THE CAR NOW.

35:17.245 --> 35:20.118
THINK YOU'RE A BIG MAN,
DO YOU?

35:20.118 --> 35:24.774
YOU REALLY THINK I'D LET YOU
GET AWAY WITH WHAT YOU'VE DONE?

35:24.774 --> 35:27.255
I WILL SHOOT YOU
IF YOU DON'T DO WHAT I SAY,

35:27.255 --> 35:28.387
BELIEVE ME.

35:28.387 --> 35:30.737
GO AHEAD.

35:30.737 --> 35:32.652
I DON'T THINK
YOU HAVE IT IN YOU.

35:36.569 --> 35:38.136
[ GUN CLICKS ]

35:40.747 --> 35:43.924
NOW WHO LOOKS STUPID?

35:43.924 --> 35:47.101
THE BULLET RIGSBY FIRED NEXT TO
YOU WAS THE ONLY ONE IN THE GUN.

35:47.101 --> 35:50.713
NOT A PARTICULARLY STRONG TRICK,
BUT IT GOT THE JOB DONE.

35:50.713 --> 35:53.586
WHAT YOU'RE GONNA DO NOW
IS GET YOUR SISTER

35:53.586 --> 35:55.370
TO COME OUT OF THE HOUSE
AND PUT HER HANDS ON HER HEAD.

35:59.548 --> 36:03.030
COME ON. GET OUT.

36:03.030 --> 36:04.684
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

36:04.684 --> 36:08.035
[ CAR DOOR OPENS ]

36:12.170 --> 36:13.345
COME ON.

36:14.911 --> 36:16.261
LET'S GO.

36:16.261 --> 36:17.740
CALL OUT TO YOUR SISTER

36:17.740 --> 36:21.004
AND TELL HER TO LET GRACE GO
AND COME OUT HERE.

36:21.004 --> 36:23.006
HAZEL?

36:23.006 --> 36:24.486
HAZEL!

36:24.486 --> 36:25.966
THE POLICE HAVE ME.

36:25.966 --> 36:28.490
THEY SAY YOU HAVE TO
LET THE GIRL GO AND COME OUT.

36:28.490 --> 36:30.971
Rigsby: EVERYTHING'S
GONNA BE FINE, HAZEL,

36:30.971 --> 36:32.494
EXACTLY
AS YOUR BROTHER SAYS.

36:32.494 --> 36:34.104
[ MUFFLED SHOUTING ]NO, NOW YOU SHUT UP.

36:34.104 --> 36:37.717
[ SCREAMS ]NO, SHUT UP!

36:50.077 --> 36:53.167
CALL OUT TO HER AGAIN.

36:53.167 --> 36:54.777
HAZEL?

36:57.867 --> 37:00.130
I DON'T KNOW WHERE SHE IS.
MAYBE SHE WENT OUT.

37:00.130 --> 37:02.481
HER S.U.V.'s
RIGHT THERE.

37:02.481 --> 37:04.570
HAZEL!

37:04.570 --> 37:07.964
I DON'T KNOW WHERE SHE IS.
I DON'T KNOW.

37:07.964 --> 37:10.271
[ MUFFLED SHOUTING ]

37:10.271 --> 37:12.142
[ GASPS ] THAT'S GRACE.RIGSBY.

37:12.142 --> 37:15.015
BUT, JANE, IT'S GRACE.J-JUST DON'T PANIC.

37:15.015 --> 37:16.756
YOU GO.

37:16.756 --> 37:20.150
BE CAREFUL.

37:48.135 --> 37:50.659
STAY THERE.

37:50.659 --> 37:52.574
GRACE. IT'S OKAY.[ MUFFLED SHOUTING ]

37:52.574 --> 37:54.097
EVERYTHING'S
GONNA BE OKAY.

37:54.097 --> 37:55.316
I'M GONNA
GET YOU OUT OF HERE.

37:56.230 --> 37:57.275
WHERE IS SHE?

37:57.275 --> 37:58.493
[ MUFFLED SHOUTING ]

37:58.493 --> 37:59.886
BEHIND YOU!

37:59.886 --> 38:01.714
[ GUNSHOT ]OHH!

38:01.714 --> 38:02.845
NICE SHOT, HAZEL!

38:02.845 --> 38:04.673
[ GROANS ]DON'T MOVE.

38:05.761 --> 38:08.068
IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT.
I PROMISE.

38:08.068 --> 38:10.288
Van Pelt: WAYNE!THIS ISN'T A TRICK GUN,
IS IT?

38:10.288 --> 38:11.898
NO!IF I SHOOT THIS ONE,

38:11.898 --> 38:13.595
A REAL BULLET WILL COME OUT,
WON'T IT?

38:13.595 --> 38:15.205
[ CRYING ]

38:15.205 --> 38:16.859
WAYNE!

38:16.859 --> 38:18.818
[ GASPS ] NO. NO.

38:18.818 --> 38:20.298
[ GROANS ]

38:20.298 --> 38:21.951
NO! NO, WAYNE!

38:23.562 --> 38:25.564
WAYNE?
Richard: WELL...

38:25.564 --> 38:27.217
THERE WAS AT LEAST ONE.[ CRYING ]

38:27.217 --> 38:31.134
LET'S GO HAVE SOME FUN.
UNTIE HER AND BRING HER ALONG.

38:31.134 --> 38:33.049
COME ON.

38:45.975 --> 38:48.978
GO ON.

38:48.978 --> 38:51.024
GO LEFT.

38:54.723 --> 38:57.073
LEFT AGAIN.

38:57.073 --> 39:01.948
WHY SO QUIET, MR. SMARTY?
CAT GOT YOUR TONGUE?

39:01.948 --> 39:05.908
YOU ALWAYS HAVE AN ANSWER FOR
EVERYTHING, USUALLY, DON'T YOU?

39:05.908 --> 39:10.260
GO ON. GO AHEAD.
KNEEL DOWN.

39:10.260 --> 39:13.568
RIGHT HERE.
GO AHEAD.

39:19.008 --> 39:22.185
I THOUGHT WE COULD PLAY
A LITTLE GAME.

39:22.185 --> 39:23.752
LIKE A QUIZ SHOW.[ GUN COCKS ]

39:24.840 --> 39:26.189
I'D ASK QUESTIONS...

39:26.189 --> 39:27.930
[ WHIMPERS ]

39:27.930 --> 39:30.672
...AND YOU GET TO KEEP A FINGER
FOR EVERY RIGHT ANSWER.

39:30.672 --> 39:32.979
I'D RATHER NOT.OKAY, FIRST QUESTION --

39:32.979 --> 39:34.676
WHO'S SMARTER NOW?

39:34.676 --> 39:36.417
I DON'T WANT TO.
YOU OR ME?

39:36.417 --> 39:37.810
I DON'T --
I DON'T WANT TO.

39:37.810 --> 39:39.725
NO ANSWER? OKAY.

39:40.682 --> 39:42.292
[ GRUNTS ][ GASPS ]

39:42.292 --> 39:43.903
Van Pelt: WAYNE!

39:46.166 --> 39:47.994
[ CRYING ][ SIGHS ]

39:47.994 --> 39:49.343
WAYNE.
OH, GOD, WAYNE.

39:49.343 --> 39:51.258
[ BOTH CRYING ]

39:51.258 --> 39:53.565
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ][ HELICOPTER BLADES WHIRRING ]

40:16.936 --> 40:19.286
WE NEED TO GET
TO A HOSPITAL.
YEAH.

40:22.463 --> 40:24.683
AND THEN HAIBACH SHOT YOU
A SECOND TIME?

40:24.683 --> 40:26.859
YEAH. THAT ONE HURT.
[ SIGHS ]

40:26.859 --> 40:28.338
BUT YOU GOT BACK UP,
DISARMED THE SISTER,

40:28.338 --> 40:30.340
AND STOPPED HAIBACH.

40:30.340 --> 40:31.864
NICE WORK, WAYNE.

40:31.864 --> 40:33.431
HE SAID HE WAS GONNA SAVE ME,
AND HE DID.

40:33.431 --> 40:35.911
YOU DO REALIZE YOU GOT SHOT
WITH YOUR OWN GUN.

40:35.911 --> 40:38.174
OH, PLEASE, CHO, NO JOKES.
IT HURTS WHEN I LAUGH.

40:38.174 --> 40:40.176
NO, I'M JUST SAYING, IF YOU TELL
THAT STORY IN THE FUTURE,

40:40.176 --> 40:41.743
YOU MIGHT WANT TO LEAVE
THAT PART OUT.

40:41.743 --> 40:43.397
SERIOUSLY,
I'M GONNA SPLIT A STITCH.

40:43.397 --> 40:44.746
[ LAUGHTER ]

40:44.746 --> 40:47.662
WE SHOULD GO,
LET YOU GET SOME REST.

40:48.576 --> 40:50.883
I DON'T KNOW WHAT WE WOULD HAVE
DONE IF WE'D LOST YOU.

40:50.883 --> 40:52.841
I KNEW
YOU GUYS WOULD COME.

40:52.841 --> 40:54.974
BYE.

40:58.194 --> 41:01.633
YOU TWO TAKE VERY GOOD CARE
OF EACH OTHER.

41:03.765 --> 41:05.071
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

41:05.071 --> 41:07.595
OH. DIDN'T MEAN
TO INTERRUPT.

41:07.595 --> 41:10.729
OH, WE WERE, UH...
JUST LEAVING.

41:10.729 --> 41:12.339
BYE.

41:15.908 --> 41:18.563
I WANTED TO COME BY
AND SEE HOW YOU'RE DOING.

41:18.563 --> 41:20.478
THANK YOU.

41:20.478 --> 41:22.001
Abbott: AND TO LET YOU
KNOW THAT YOU IMPRESSED
THE HELL OUT OF US.

41:22.001 --> 41:25.134
NOT TOO MANY PEOPLE
CAN DO WHAT YOU DID.

41:25.134 --> 41:27.267
[ SIGHS ]
THANK YOU. REALLY.

41:27.267 --> 41:29.922
WE'RE JUST GLAD
THAT YOU'RE BOTH OKAY.

41:29.922 --> 41:32.272
YEAH.

41:32.272 --> 41:34.013
YEAH.

41:35.667 --> 41:37.538
AND IF YOU TWO
EVER THINK ABOUT

41:37.538 --> 41:39.497
GETTING BACK
TO OUR SIDE OF THE BUSINESS,

41:39.497 --> 41:40.889
GIVE ME A CALL.

41:40.889 --> 41:43.370
I DON'T THINK SO.

41:44.589 --> 41:46.329
CIVILIAN LIFE,
HERE WE COME.

41:46.329 --> 41:48.723
WELL, THAT'S TOO BAD.

41:48.723 --> 41:50.769
ANYHOW,
THE OFFER'S STILL OPEN.

41:50.769 --> 41:51.770
THANK YOU.
THANK YOU.

41:51.770 --> 41:52.771
Fischer: TAKE CARE.

41:52.771 --> 41:54.773
BYE.

41:54.773 --> 41:57.079
OKAY.
I'M GONNA HEAD OUT, TOO.

41:57.079 --> 42:00.430
OH, DON'T GO YET, BUDDY.
GOT LUNCH COMING UP.

42:00.430 --> 42:02.084
I CAN GET YOU YOUR OWN.

42:02.084 --> 42:04.217
HOSPITAL LUNCH?

42:04.217 --> 42:08.047
IT'S REALLY NOT THAT BAD.
THEY GOT CHERRY COBBLER.

42:12.921 --> 42:15.228
Lisbon: I WAS REALLY ANGRY
AT YOU FOR DOING WHAT YOU DID,

42:15.228 --> 42:16.708
BUT THEN
I THOUGHT BETTER OF IT.

42:16.708 --> 42:19.014
IT WAS A STUPID IDEA,
BUT, HEY, IT WORKED.

42:19.014 --> 42:21.016
WHOA. STUPID?
NOT NECESSARILY STUPID.

42:21.016 --> 42:22.670
SIMPLE. NOT STUPID.

42:22.670 --> 42:24.150
BUT I AM
STILL ANGRY AT YOU

42:24.150 --> 42:25.412
FOR NOT TELLING ME
WHAT YOU WERE GONNA DO.

42:25.412 --> 42:26.413
I THOUGHT
YOU'D GONE NUTS.

42:26.413 --> 42:27.936
OH, COME ON, PLEASE.

42:27.936 --> 42:29.459
IT'S NOT LIKE I HAVEN'T ABDUCTED
PEOPLE BEFORE.

42:29.459 --> 42:31.940
IT'S NOT FUNNY.
I WAS REALLY SCARED.

42:31.940 --> 42:33.289
I'M SORRY.

42:33.289 --> 42:34.813
NO, YOU'RE NOT.

42:34.813 --> 42:36.510
I CAN TELL WHEN
YOU'RE NOT BEING SINCERE NOW.

42:36.510 --> 42:38.817
WELL, CLEARLY, YOU CAN'T,
BECAUSE I AMSORRY.

42:38.817 --> 42:40.514
I CAN TELL JUST BY LOOKING
AT YOU, OKAY?

42:40.514 --> 42:42.560
BUT YOU CAN'T SEE
WHAT I'M FEELING.
